# UI Consistency

Keep the app visually and behaviorally consistent. Reuse before reinventing.

## Design system (required)

Use shared primitives from `src/components/ui/`:

- `Button`, `Input`, `Textarea`, `Select`, `Card`, `Badge`
- `Loader`, `Skeleton`, `EmptyState`, `Toast`

Do **not** create raw `<button>` / `<input>` with custom styles unless extending the design system itself.

## Theme tokens

Colors, radius, and shadows come from `src/styles/theme.css`. Use Tailwind semantic tokens:

- `bg-secondary`, `text-secondary`, `border-border`, `text-muted`, `text-foreground`
- `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl` for cards and surfaces

Never hardcode hex colors in components. Update `theme.css` for brand changes.

## Mobile-first layout (required)

Write default styles for mobile, then add breakpoints:

- Grids: `grid-cols-1` → `md:grid-cols-2` → `lg:grid-cols-3`
- Flex: `flex-col` → `md:flex-row` when side-by-side makes sense on larger screens
- Hide/show: `hidden md:block` only if mobile users have an equivalent path (menu, drawer, stacked layout)
- CTAs: `w-full md:w-auto` for primary buttons on forms and booking flows

## Layout patterns

- **Public/marketing**: single-column on mobile; `CoachingCard` grids stack then expand; one hero CTA above the fold on phone.
- **Dashboards**: `DashboardSidebar` stacks above content on mobile (`w-full md:w-64`); page actions in a vertical stack on small screens.
- **Forms**: single column on mobile; label above field; full-width submit; `React Hook Form` + inline errors.

## Spacing and typography

- Page padding: `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8` (never less than `px-4` on mobile).
- Headings: page `text-2xl font-bold`, section `text-lg font-semibold`, body `text-sm text-muted`.
- Cards: `rounded-xl border border-border bg-white shadow-sm p-5`.

## Motion

Use subtle transitions (`transition duration-300`, hover lift on cards). Avoid distracting animations on forms or dashboards.

## Checklist for new UI

- [ ] **Mobile-first**: works at 320–390px before desktop polish
- [ ] Uses existing `ui/` components
- [ ] Matches spacing/typography of a similar page in the same route group
- [ ] Has loading, empty, and error states
- [ ] Tappable targets ≥ 44px; no hover-only interactions
